      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 buyers should know upfront that this car has significant issues. The exterior shows substantial wear including dents, scratches, and rust in multiple areas. The interior is worn and damaged, with tears in the upholstery and non-functional components. Mechanically, the car has known problems that will require serious attention and repair work before it can be considered reliably roadworthy. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or seeking parts. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects the true state of the vehicle.",
