      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Solid & Road-Ready \u2014 A Practical Pick at an Honest Price! \ud83d\ude99 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it gets the job done and handles everyday driving reliably! The exterior shows some signs of wear including minor scratches and small blemishes that come with regular use, and the interior is functional with visible signs of age. Mechanically, it runs well and is ready to take on your daily commute or errands without fuss! If you're looking for dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price, this one deserves a look. Come take it for a spin!",
